Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要文化遗产调查？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不能在规定时间内完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种景点怎么可能有任务嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想约我去玩就直说好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是去玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很认真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 跟我一起接受这个任务吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风很诚心地请伊札那和他去两天一夜的旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是去千秋乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是千秋乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 凑近一点看更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊…伊札那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道…
